{"tid":589690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"原來區諾軒喺傳統建制票倉北角都冇慘敗到","createTime":"2018-03-12T04:28:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-12T04:59:36.000Z","uid":136994,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"14bb600b5f7cb863244439b0d396629c08d833e3","tid":589690,"uid":136994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:28:27.000Z","msg":"北角有六個主要選區<br />\n區諾軒只喺輸咗最大嘅和富選區，同城市花園輸咗十幾票，其他選區都竟然係區諾軒有多啲票<br />\n反而姚松炎喺啲深水埗土瓜灣舊區同新移民邨就真係慘敗啦<br />\n所以新移民真係畀福建幫有更大影響力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n班泛民甚至本土幾時先識得去呢啲地方深耕細作，拎多啲樁腳箍地方票？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/03/12/122527_2ae1b7eb7aa573a6199a264bf395ee44.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F03%2F12%2F122527_2ae1b7eb7aa573a6199a264bf395ee44.png&h=3e558710&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c637ecab7a52c969999bf767f7c0ebe9f83078fb","tid":589690,"uid":11719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"港島區化仲未被蝗化"},{"pid":"4e121617e443ada73d4c8f32c188a40e3e10c59a","tid":589690,"uid":38651,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:30:36.000Z","msg":"北角黎講真係唔差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 估唔到錦屏會贏<br />\n丹拿就公民黨地頭 贏係正常<br />\n城市花園就算鳩數啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee966425b5d51cbff3f9f3025e7d6f0952b232fa","tid":589690,"uid":49643,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-12T04:31:43.000Z","msg":"支持開民建聯唔見得一定要支持新民黨喎，就算有動員都會留返d唔會去盡"},{"pid":"9142c3169b35ae2ea6aa2d7ca52727dcc22fe0d1","tid":589690,"uid":11719,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"r